<br>
I just switched from hammer to axe and am a total convert. For positionals, the Evernight/Arctic rift rear is great in both PvE and RvR, if you can maneuver for the rear attack, assisting a main tank. And if you go for the 50 Axe/43 BS/2 Parry spec, Havoc/Tyr's fury from the front catches some unprepared from a Skald.<br>
<br>
(Also love Evernight/Arctic rift on fleeing bards/minstrels...)<br>
<br>
With a Shaman's end buff, it's fun to finally do a continuous stream of decent damage.<br>
