<br>
I think Hammer wins if you need to conserve End usage (provoke's low End usage seems like a data bug never corrected).<br>
<br>
I think Hammer wins if you want to concentrate on runners and rear positionals.  Conquer snares!  No more runners!  To get a snare with an axe you will need to land Pillager then Plunder (and ignore Evernight/Arctic Rift).<br>
<br>
Hammer seems to win if you want effects like snare and stun.  Hammer has a stun off an anytime style, while axe requires a parry to stun.<br>
<br>
Axe seems to have the highest straight up fighting damage though.  While you are mashing the 0.58 Provoke, Axe users are probably mashing Havoc/Tyr's for 0.75 then 0.94.  If axe users can't get Havoc to land, we are losing a lot of damage and Hammer looks better because Provoke uses less End than Plague.<br>
<br>
Finally, I think most of our enemies take more damage from the axe slashing weapon than the hammer crush weapon, if you look at the armor resist charts?<br>
<br>
-Leitari, MLF <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=535.topic&start=21&stop=30>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=535.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=535.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=535.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=535.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.threadControl?topicID=535.topic><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/closethread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=535.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=535.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub36.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForu